      • OTHER

        public static final JRE OTHER
        A JRE version other than JAVA_8, JAVA_9, JAVA_10, or JAVA_11.

        Note that OTHER will be considered to be the current JRE version if the current JRE version could not be detected — for example, if the java.version JVM system property is undefined.
